OL,5,
OL,6,CG2018FHave I Got News for You is the
OL,7,Ffinal programme to be recorded at The
OL,8,FLondon Studios before the complex is
OL,9,Fclosed down ahead of demolition work.
OL,10,
OL,11,FOn 21st February 2017, it was announced
OL,12,Fthat ITV would be closing the site in
OL,13,Fmid-2018 for five years due to
OL,14,Flarge-scale redevelopment of the site.
